<varlistentry id="options.RplayHost">
	<term>RplayHost <emphasis remap='I'>"hostname"</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
	<para>Specifies what host the sounds will play on.  The  hostname  can
        also  be  an  environment  variable  such  as $HOSTDISPLAY. This
        option is only valid with builtin rplay support. If this is left
        out  then  Audio  will attempt to connect to rplay daemon on the
        same host that is running X first, then to localhost.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
